{"tid":428054,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"ASUS主機板居亞太區首位　全球市佔率達 45%","createTime":"2017-10-07T19:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T16:00:07.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b2fe26f8293939e2fb66fb51266bc6f31bd90a36","tid":428054,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T19:01:05.000Z","msg":"ASUS 主機板在全球市場一直佔優<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最近全球市佔率更飆升至 45%<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其中以 X299 及 Z270 等高端產品線尤為暢銷。據台灣媒體 DIGITIMES 報導，華碩的高階主機板在美國、歐洲及日本成為市場主導；而在新西蘭、澳洲、印度及一些亞太區國家如菲律賓、印尼、泰國、越南、馬來西亞及星加坡，華碩主機板銷量更位居市場首位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/RED_0603-710x473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2FRED_0603-710x473.jpg&h=a1bb916b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2017/10/03/華碩主機板居亞太區首位-全球市佔率達-45/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F%E8%8F%AF%E7%A2%A9%E4%B8%BB%E6%A9%9F%E6%9D%BF%E5%B1%85%E4%BA%9E%E5%A4%AA%E5%8D%80%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%B8%82%E4%BD%94%E7%8E%87%E9%81%94-45%2F&d=TtaPMzyvtoMN0LA7bR7Blv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=c4f953cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2017/10/03/華碩主機板居亞太區首位-全球市佔率達-45/</a></div>"},{"pid":"8af514468e40606cd5b291b0ca397e9d004aa146","tid":428054,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T19:01:56.000Z","msg":"華碩 X299 系列主機板在亞太區高端市場有多達 70% 市佔率，Z270 系列也在電競主機板市場佔 60%。消息指，受亞太區的主機板銷量帶動，華碩的收入及盈利都有所增長。<br />\n<br />\n隨著 Intel 第八代 Coffee Lake CPU 在 10 月 5 日解禁，華碩將在第四季推出一系列 Z370 晶片的主機板，包括 Prime、ROG 及 TUF 三個產品線，其中有 8 款為 ROG- 及 ROG Strix- 電競系列，以鞏固她在電競主機板的地位。受新產品發佈推動，華碩期望在 2017 年第四季及 2018 年的業績能繼續穩步上揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，市佔率亦比 Gigabyte 及 MSI 等競爭對手遙遙領先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"8445dd67c362facba5fb03a1c2d83758d4830548","tid":428054,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3850aaa43cfbbeaa807b843b2bb637343f60d3a","tid":428054,"uid":4754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T03:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc0f463b20b13d3dd005963ac23fed033743feb","tid":428054,"uid":20352,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T04:18:55.000Z","msg":"準備有班人入黎話asus版點唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457a8efac0c914c65cfb5915845194f17bbcfdc9","tid":428054,"uid":124537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:20:35.000Z","msg":"以卵擊石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568eef8e05097cc6475246539324946f619c4d48","tid":428054,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>準備有班人入黎話asus版點唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔計價錢貴,用開冇問題<br />\n顯示卡同底板都係"},{"pid":"d8e7b329075a4d2a146d5d2f54d75ba4ae4d13a0","tid":428054,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:53:58.000Z","msg":"ROG 唔錯喎<br />\n利申 用緊asus"},{"pid":"f6a32740d1104c92eed6d9a607525d29505829c1","tid":428054,"uid":124537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:28:27.000Z","msg":"